# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AGENTRA Environment Variables Template
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.dev, .env.staging, or .env.prod and fill in your values.
# These values will be loaded by the deployment script (deploy.ps1).
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit .env files with actual secrets to source control!
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Azure OpenAI Configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are provisioned automatically by Bicep, but you can override if using
# an existing Azure OpenAI resource.
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-openai.openai.azure.com/
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key
# AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4o

# ── Optional: Anthropic Claude (for Claude execution mode) ────────────────────
# Leave empty if not using Claude mode
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Optional: AI Foundry Connection ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Azure AI Foundry project connection string for AI Foundry execution mode
# AI_FOUNDRY_CONNECTION_STRING=

# ── Database Configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cosmos DB is provisioned by Bicep. Override only if using existing resources.
# COSMOS_DB_ENDPOINT=https://your-cosmos.documents.azure.com:443/
# COSMOS_DB_KEY=your-cosmos-key

# ── Storage Configuration ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Storage account for document generation. Provisioned by Bicep.
# STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING=DefaultEndpointsProtocol=https;...

# ── External Database Connections (for MCP Server) ────────────────────────────
# Add connection strings for databases you want to connect to for data migration.
# Format: DBTYPE_CONNECTIONSTRING_NAME=connection-string
#
# SQL Server
# SQLSERVER_SOURCE_DB=Server=myserver.database.windows.net;Database=mydb;User Id=user;Password=pass;
#
# PostgreSQL
# POSTGRES_SOURCE_DB=postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/database
#
# MySQL
# MYSQL_SOURCE_DB=mysql://user:pass@host:3306/database
#
# Oracle
# ORACLE_SOURCE_DB=oracle://user:pass@host:1521/service
#
# MongoDB
# MONGODB_SOURCE_DB=mongodb://user:pass@host:27017/database
#
# Snowflake
# SNOWFLAKE_ACCOUNT=your-account
# SNOWFLAKE_USER=your-user
# SNOWFLAKE_PASSWORD=your-password
# SNOWFLAKE_WAREHOUSE=your-warehouse
#
# Databricks
# DATABRICKS_HOST=https://your-workspace.azuredatabricks.net
# DATABRICKS_TOKEN=your-token
#
# BigQuery
# BIGQUERY_PROJECT_ID=your-project
# BIGQUERY_CREDENTIALS_JSON=path/to/credentials.json
